            <p><strong>Subject:</strong> GameBond - Privacy Policy</p>
        </div>

        <h2>12. Data Minimization</h2>
        <p>We follow the principle of data minimization, especially important for family apps:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>We only collect information that is necessary for GameBond to function properly</li>
            <li>We don't collect sensitive personal information beyond what's required</li>
            <li>We regularly review what data we collect and delete unnecessary information</li>
            <li>Most personal preferences and game data remain on your family's device</li>
            <li>We prioritize local storage over cloud storage for family data</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>13. Family Safety Commitment</h2>
        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Our Commitment to Family Safety:</strong> GameBond is committed to creating a safe, private environment for families to bond and have fun together. We continuously review our privacy practices to ensure they meet the highest standards for family-oriented applications.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Safety Features:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Family-appropriate content filters and moderation</li>
            <li>Age-appropriate activity suggestions</li>
            <li>Parental controls for content customization</li>
            <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
            <li>Transparent privacy practices</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Questions About Privacy?</strong> We're here to help your family use GameBond safely and privately. If you have any questions about how we protect your family's privacy or handle your data, don't hesitate to contact us. Your family's trust is important to us.</p>
